newsitem.title: EU: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ C 255 OF SEPTEMBER 3, 1996.
newsitem.headline: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ C 255 OF SEPTEMBER 3, 1996.

text.p: (Note - contents are displayed in reverse order to that in the printed Journal)
EUROPEAN ECONOMIC INTEREST GROUPING Notices published pursuant to Council Regulation (EEC) No 2137/85 of 25 July 1985 - Formation
Corrigendum to the notice of initiation of an anti-dumping proceeding concerning imports of briefcases and schoolbags originating in the People's Republic of China
Prior notification of a concentration (Addendum) (Case No IV/M.820 - British Aerospace/Lagardere SCA)
Communication regarding Commission recommendation of 30 July 1996 on the use of the Common Procurement Vocabulary (CPV) for describing the subject-matter of public contracts
Notice pursuant to Article 19 (3) of Council Regulation 17 concerning a request for negative clearance or an exemption pursuant to Article 85 (3) of the EC Treaty (Case IV/35.518 - Iridium)
Rate of interest applied by the European Monetary Institute for its operations in ecus: 4,25 % for September 1996 Ecu END OF DOCUMENT.
